In [4]:
del df["Unnamed: 0"]

df['Area sqF'] = df['Area SqM']*10.7639

del df['Area SqM']

def haversine_vectorize(lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2):

    lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2 = map(np.radians, [lon1, lat1, lon2, lat2])

    newlon = lon2 - lon1
    newlat = lat2 - lat1

    haver_formula = np.sin(newlat/2.0)**2 + np.cos(lat1) * np.cos(lat2) * np.sin(newlon/2.0)**2

    dist = 2 * np.arcsin(np.sqrt(haver_formula ))
    km = 6367 * dist #6367 for distance in KM for miles use 3958
    return km

df['Distance'] = haversine_vectorize(df['Longitude'], df['Latitude'], 74.331474, 31.504499)

df['Ppsqft'] = df['Price']/df['Area sqF']

df = df.reindex(['Latitude','Longitude','Distance','Price','Area sqF','Ppsqft','Zameen ID','Title','Purpose','PhotoCount',
                                 'VideoCount','Agency ID','Agency Product','Is Verified','Product Score','Location','Type'], axis=1)

df['Location']= df['Location'].str[8:]

del df['VideoCount']

del df['Is Verified']

del df['PhotoCount']

df = df.dropna()

df['Product Score']= df['Product Score'].astype(np.int64)

df['Distance'] = df['Distance'].astype(np.int64)

price_ranges = [
    {'range': (0, 5000000), 'color': 'blue'},
    {'range': (5000000, 10000000), 'color': 'green'},
    {'range': (10000000, 20000000), 'color': 'yellow'},
    {'range': (20000000, 50000000), 'color': 'orange'},
    {'range': (50000000, 100000000), 'color': 'red'},
    {'range': (100000000, 2710000000), 'color': 'purple'}]

colormap = StepColormap(
    colors=[range_dict['color'] for range_dict in price_ranges],
    index=[range_dict['range'][0] for range_dict in price_ranges] + [price_ranges[-1]['range'][1]],
    vmin=0,
    vmax=2710000000,
    caption='Price Range'
)

colormap.caption='Price Range'

    color = colormap(price)
    folium.CircleMarker(
        location=[latitude, longitude],
        radius=5,
        color=color,
        fill=True,
        fill_color=color,
        fill_opacity=0.7
    ).add_to(map)
